      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>meat-free mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!) to the pan and cook for 5-6 min<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>or until browned, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p><p>Add your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>and <strong>tomato paste </strong>and stir to combine</p><p>Add 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[325ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>with your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish </strong>and<strong> </strong>1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>or until slightly thickened</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
