    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>cooked potatoes</strong> to a medium heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>rosemary leaves</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Lightly crush the potatoes with a masher or fork and then give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>rosemary potatoes</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't press too hard, you only want to crush them!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
