    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince mixture has thickened, season with a grind of<strong> pepper </strong>and discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong>, transfer it to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> and reserve the pan</p><p>Top the meat-free mince mixture with the <strong>rosemary potatoes </strong>and sprinkle over the<strong> reserved rosemary leaves</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 20 min<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>or until golden and bubbling – this is your<strong> hearty meat-free mince</strong>,<strong> carrot & mustard pie</strong></p>",
